# All CVEs below are in transitive dependencies where npm audit fix --force
# would require breaking major version downgrades (NestJS 11→10, Nx 22→20).
# Reviewed and accepted as low risk for a private family app.

# path-to-regexp in @nestjs/core — DoS via regex, awaiting NestJS patch
CVE-2026-4926

# minimatch — DoS via unbounded backtracking, in npm/tar transitive dep
CVE-2026-27903
CVE-2026-27904

# tar — path traversal via symlinks, in npm internals
CVE-2026-29786
CVE-2026-31802

# picomatch — ReDoS via extglob, bundled in node:24-alpine's npm (not app code)
CVE-2026-33671

# zlib in Alpine base — buffer overflow, awaiting nginx-unprivileged image update
CVE-2026-22184
